channel.title: Wondering
channel.description:
I'm trying to get back into Diablo 2 for some fun with friends, and I've got the first part of the game all squared away. The problem is that I've lost my cd-key to the expansion, I've got the disk and all - was just wondering if there is anyone on here that could supply me with a working cd-key. I'm not going to be playing a lot or anything, it's just the fact that I can't play with my friends atm... and where I live it is pretty expensive to get it shipped (can't seem to find anywhere to just buy a cd-key online)
If anyone can help...I'd be more than glad.
